---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const breadcrumbSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "FAQs", "item": "https://sydneyanxietypsychology.com.au/faq/" },
  ]
};
---
<Base
  title="Common Questions | Telehealth Anxiety Psychology Sydney | FAQ"
  description="Answers to common questions about finding a psychologist for anxiety in Sydney: session numbers, Medicare telehealth rebates, wait times, and the difference between psychologists and psychiatrists."
  schema={[breadcrumbSchema]}
>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="container">

      <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; Common Questions
      </p>

      <h1>Common Questions About Anxiety Psychology in Sydney</h1>

      <p>Quick answers to the questions we see most often from people in Sydney looking for a psychologist for anxiety.</p>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0;">

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;"><a href="/faq/how-many-sessions-do-i-need-for-anxiety/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">How many sessions do I need for anxiety?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">What the evidence says about therapy duration for anxiety disorders, Medicare's 10-session limit, and how to think about ongoing treatment.</p>
          <a href="/faq/how-many-sessions-do-i-need-for-anxiety/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the answer &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;"><a href="/faq/does-medicare-cover-telehealth-psychology/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">Does Medicare cover telehealth psychology sessions?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Yes — telehealth psychology attracts the same Medicare rebate as in-person. Here is exactly how it works, what the rebate is, and what to ask your GP.</p>
          <a href="/faq/does-medicare-cover-telehealth-psychology/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the answer &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;"><a href="/faq/psychologist-wait-times-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">How long is the wait to see a psychologist in Sydney?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Wait times vary widely by suburb, modality, and practitioner. Here is what drives wait times and how to reduce yours.</p>
          <a href="/faq/psychologist-wait-times-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the answer &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box" style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 1.5rem;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.1rem;"><a href="/faq/psychologist-vs-psychiatrist-sydney/" style="text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text);">What is the difference between a psychologist and a psychiatrist?</a></h2>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">Training, Medicare pathways, what each treats, and how to know which is right for you — particularly for anxiety.</p>
          <a href="/faq/psychologist-vs-psychiatrist-sydney/" style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent);">Read the answer &rarr;</a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <p>More detailed information on costs, the Medicare pathway, and how to choose a psychologist is in the <a href="/guides/">guides section</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
